tool_description: Create a shipment, get rates and generate shipping labels.
name: Shippo
title: Shippo

api_list.name: getSingleManifest
api_list.description: Retrieves single manifest from the list of manifests.

required_parameters.name: apiKey
required_parameters.description: The api key obtained from Shippo.

required_parameters.name: manifestId
required_parameters.description: Id of the manifest.

api_list.name: createAddress

required_parameters.name: city
required_parameters.description: City of the address.

required_parameters.name: objectPurpose
required_parameters.description: Purpose of the new address. Possible valuse: QUOTE or PURCHASE.

required_parameters.name: apiKey
required_parameters.description: The api key obtained from Shippo.

required_parameters.name: street1
required_parameters.description: Street of the address.

required_parameters.name: state
required_parameters.description: State of the address, if applied (otherwise leave empty).

required_parameters.name: country
required_parameters.description: ISO 3166-1-alpha-2 code (ISO 2 country code).

required_parameters.name: zip
required_parameters.description: Zip code of the address.

required_parameters.name: name
required_parameters.description: Name for the address.

required_parameters.name: email
required_parameters.description: Email of the address.

optional_parameters.name: street2
optional_parameters.description: Optional additional info about the address.

optional_parameters.name: isResidential
optional_parameters.description: Describes if a person is residential.

optional_parameters.name: street3
optional_parameters.description: Optional additional info about the address.

optional_parameters.name: streetNo
optional_parameters.description: Optional additional info about the address.

api_list.name: createCarrierAccount

required_parameters.name: carrierName
required_parameters.description: Name of the carrier. You can find list of carriers at this page - https://goshippo.com/docs/carriers.

required_parameters.name: carrierParameters
required_parameters.description: Additional parameters for the account, such as e.g. password or token. You can find list of carriers at this page - https://goshippo.com/docs/carriers.

required_parameters.name: apiKey
required_parameters.description: The api key obtained from Shippo.

required_parameters.name: carrierAccountId
required_parameters.description: Unique identifier of the account. You can find list of carriers at this page - https://goshippo.com/docs/carriers.

optional_parameters.name: carrierAccountActive
optional_parameters.description: Determines whether the account is enabled. Default is enabled.

api_list.name: createCustomsDeclaration

required_parameters.name: declarationCertifySigner
required_parameters.description: Certify signer

required_parameters.name: apiKey
required_parameters.description: The api key obtained from Shippo.

required_parameters.name: certify
required_parameters.description: Sets certify

required_parameters.name: declarationContentsType
required_parameters.description: Type of items. Possible values: DOCUMENTS, GIFT, SAMPLE, MERCHANDISE, HUMANITARIAN, DONATION, RETURN, OTHER

required_parameters.name: declarationNonDeliveryOption
required_parameters.description: Options is case of non delivery. Possible values: ABANDON OR RETURN

required_parameters.name: declarationItems
required_parameters.description: Ids of items icluded in declaration

optional_parameters.name: declarationContentsExplanation
optional_parameters.description: Explanatin of items content. Required only if declarationContentsType is OTHER

required_parameters.name: itemWeightMeasurementUnit

required_parameters.name: itemNetWeight
required_parameters.description: Net weight of the item

required_parameters.description: Address of the sender

required_parameters.name: shipmentObjectPurpose

required_parameters.name: serviceLevelToken
required_parameters.description: Specific rates when purchasing shipping label. Possible values are described at this page: https://goshippo.com/docs/reference#servicelevels

optional_parameters.name: labelFileType
optional_parameters.description: Filetypes of the label. Possible values: PNG, PDF, PDF_4X6,ZPLII
